<subSubSection id="6ECE486DF0019B574CF3D04E0F82848E" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" type="holotype">
<paragraph id="9403F6D339A10FCA3106E6F9E729EB86" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Holotype.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="0D4AAD50B854DF5990A6A6300FAE5713" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">
Turkey, Prov. Antalya, distr. Kemer (Lycia): 
<normalizedToken id="136DDE245D3A51766381C5E44CF6408D" originalValue="Gönük">Goenuek</normalizedToken>
, by dry stream bed, 7 Jul 1949, 
<emphasis id="F997D91761F972777F1F991800C2C390" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Davis</emphasis>
, 
<emphasis id="615726D4C1EEA9C323E0F653408D4373" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">
Bilger &amp; Attila 
<taxonomicName id="E5FDB693A9CB10B678326277EEC20A47" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="D." kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="D." order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">D.</taxonomicName>
15009
</emphasis>
(K-000077456!; isotype: E-00301891!).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="F49A940BAE7ABFB77DC981CCF038F0EB" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" type="notes">
<paragraph id="AABF9CB62643742D4EEC019061C28507" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="91ED6137B53AA5AF87441BA18AC06376" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">
The name 
<taxonomicName id="91E1A101C32FE13573DC39425E9DD546" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Dianthus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Dianthus tunicoides" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="tunicoides">
<emphasis id="4976236ED71A9CACF58B781686C37F56" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Dianthus tunicoides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Madhani &amp; Heubl in Taxon 67(1): 103. 2018) was already published as a new name for 
<taxonomicName id="C8A746C62AC99595CF7DFD5324D5BD40" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Caryophyllaceae" genus="Gypsophila" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Gypsophila armerioides" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="armerioides">
<emphasis id="DA872DA8885513C2992FAD8EC1108C44" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Gypsophila armerioides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Ser. ex DC. ≡ 
<taxonomicName id="EA7BA8AC3305C7FFFB7504789EA89A75" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Amaranthaceae" genus="Petrorhagia" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Petrorhagia armerioides" order="Caryophyllales" pageId="0" pageNumber="91" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="armerioides">
<emphasis id="6D348A3B23DE69778E990C5DFDFDC01B" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="91">Petrorhagia armerioides</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Ser. ex DC.) P.W.Ball &amp; Heywood. This new name refers to the province of Antalya, Turkey, from where the species was described.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
